Alfresco is an enterprise content platform that you can use in the cloud or behind your firewall. It helps you store and share the documents that every business depends on. Alfresco is built for the portability of the tablet and the power of the cloud.Now you can work anywhere, with anyone, on any device—all connected by the cloud. In other words, Alfresco makes sure you have your content wherever you are.This solution provides automated installation and configuration for Alfresco Enterprise 4.0.1 (Standalone Configuration) as a service.Alfresco works the way you do. It allows you and your content to move from desktop to cloud to tablet to Smartphone. Wherever you are—access your files and share them with those who need them.
   
 

    
 